Implement a reasonable toString() on the BundleNode implementations.  Unfortunately, in the case of a MessageResources object from Struts, it's not possible to get the list of message keys, so it's impossible to implement entrySet() on Map.  The toString() has a reasonable default message and shouldn't stack trace any longer.
